Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼才相信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.27,0:03:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…同伴们…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚还说说笑笑的家伙们…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.02,0:03:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解  会报仇雪恨的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.89,0:03:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底…是谁向A-LAWS泄的密
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.49,0:03:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你都干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,A-LAWS的间谍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不是  我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.53,0:03:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我事情的原委  沙慈·克洛斯罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙  这就是他们的做法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:57.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:03:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,米蕾娜不能看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生于战火  又魂归战火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:06.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这就是所谓的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这就是所谓的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:11.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不得不战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.81,0:04:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,生于战火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是友军
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.58,0:04:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又魂归战火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这就是所谓的命运…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就不得不战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,踏上望不到尽头的征程
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,路的尽头…就是生命的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:41.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是神的指引
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.81,0:04:46.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米里奥…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:49.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米里奥！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:54.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:55.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,皇小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:05:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你都…干了什么蠢事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.28,0:05:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没料到会有这种结果…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.27,0:05:09.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想逃离战争而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生这种事…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,夺走他们生命的就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是你愚蠢的举动造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把自己当作局外人  与自己无关
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,视之为不同的世界的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种逃避现实的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不自觉地变成恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最终招致这样的后果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:36.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我也不想这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特瑞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:41.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,A-LAWS干得好事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而原因在于他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.07,0:05:53.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙慈·克洛斯罗德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不回阿扎提斯坦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.51,0:06:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,席琳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿扎提斯坦…我们的故国被…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:08.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿扎提斯坦被…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说失去了Gundam的去向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但对反联邦政府秘密基地的打击却取得成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是大功一件啊  马内金上校
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:24.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  您讨厌扫荡战吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是乐在其中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:31.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说在享受杀人的乐趣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.44,0:06:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用这么激动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您以前不是也做过同样的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  那可是惨剧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:47.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情报出错导致友军自相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那时您应该是AEU的战术预报员…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.43,0:06:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又想对自己人动手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:07:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了那样的事  理应不再介入战争了才对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可现在却还这么留恋？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是很敬重你的哦  马内金上校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阿扎提斯坦竟然遭到了攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.09,0:07:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是联邦做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:22.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但参与进攻的MS中…有一架Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:28.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.68,0:07:31.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那架机体恐怕是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.61,0:07:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,皇小姐似乎晕倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.57,0:07:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发出了托勒密起动命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.86,0:07:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了  回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:44.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:47.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,待在这里不知道会被如何处置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:56.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都市区域的主要设施几乎全被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.29,0:08:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是警察还是军队都发挥不了作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.45,0:08:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算如此  我还是想回到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个拉撒托付给我的国家去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,幸亏你能回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是刹那强行把我带回来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要多谢他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢什么？ 我死不足惜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是为了阿扎提斯坦…我赴汤蹈火都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛丽娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Celestial Being似乎想把这里缺失的器材和食物进行紧急部署
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在其它设施尚未移送完成之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会参与防卫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  转告他们解了我们的燃眉之急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是谁泄漏了这里的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.67,0:08:51.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这问题问同是间谍的我好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新生的Celestial Being多么地友善啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:09:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是受谁的影响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.96,0:09:03.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐  由我来安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就交给妮娜·崔尼蒂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:07.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为何？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:10.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你能用脑量子波？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要骗过改革者们  少不了她的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个任务不适合你  红龙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.77,0:09:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我和那家伙没有本质区别吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.40,0:09:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由于精神打击  导致一时间意识紊乱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,过一会就会苏醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,皇小姐到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:48.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不清楚  但原因应该来自这次的残杀事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,艾米里奥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.35,0:09:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你的战术预报
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.39,0:09:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根据错误的情报你们制定了各种战术
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后导致友军间互相残杀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我十分敬重一心一意关注战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为使其迅速结束而竭尽全力的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.73,0:10:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们过于优秀了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.36,0:10:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,马内金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.08,0:10:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的…艾米里奥…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九条
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:21.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam们的战术…很像她的指挥风格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说九条她…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…不  那才是真正的战场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:45.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上校发来的密码文？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要用顶武使用的方式？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要如此转弯抹角与你联络我深表歉意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这封信不想被A-LAWS发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说中尉你参加了卡塔隆的歼灭战
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这件事  我必须向你谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢罪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为上校得到的情报  导致了这次扫荡战的实行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.85,0:11:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上校一定十分悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.20,0:11:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这时候都如此在意我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把我收为养女吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  这要征得你的同意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,索玛·斯米尔诺夫这名字果然不怎么顺耳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  不能再用佩丽丝这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我感到有一点悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你很喜欢这个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:50.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不想忘记蕴含在其中的那些往事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.21,0:11:58.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏上校我才重新认识到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.05,0:12:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自己只是超人特务机关的一号超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:07.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是杀人的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.44,0:12:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不配拥有幸福的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是失态啊  斯米尔诺夫上校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然让卡塔隆的参战员逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来我特地跑来显得…毫无意义！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上校
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然对长官出手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是政府直属的独立治安维持部队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可不要把我们与联邦军的军衔相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:35.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的责任全在我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在上级的处分下达之前  请你继续执行任务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:43.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对阿扎提斯坦的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦着手中东重编
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  这可真是惨不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法  没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.66,0:13:09.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  工作工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:24.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,巴拉克·基宁上尉等补充人员五名  前来报到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:26.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是卡蒂·马内金
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上尉  你为何会加入A-LAWS？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.50,0:13:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,报告  在下是想为世界统一尽一份力主动申请的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:35.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,皇小姐情况怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还没醒过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概还需要静养一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔隆方的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请看屏幕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卡塔隆的转移按照预定于1200开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,A-LAWS会来  毫无疑问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用Gundam迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.22,0:14:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是战术怎么办  皇小姐倒下后现在这状况…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此我们也只能上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,托勒密向海岸线移动  得让敌人发现我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.88,0:14:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,普特利麦奥斯  出发
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,针对独立治安维持部队对反政府势力的镇压作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:54.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全球各地爆发了报复性恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的行为  竟然演变这种地步…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.83,0:14:59.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要怎么做才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  路易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,解除光学迷彩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.74,0:15:12.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本舰被监视卫星捕捉到的时间推定为0037
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.11,0:15:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全员  做好一级战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是超兵  任何任务都要忠实地执行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.35,0:15:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为此而被创造出来的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.94,0:15:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰到您了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:41.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在下是作为补充人员到任的路易丝·哈莱维准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:45.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是MS部队所属的索玛·佩丽丝中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉  中尉大人  我随随便便就跟您说话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:52.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.60,0:15:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脑量子波是这样感觉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.53,0:16:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的内心在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.06,0:16:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在思念着某人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉  您在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到作战会议的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是路易丝·哈莱维准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少尉  你该回礼才是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是安德烈·斯密尔诺夫少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是少女啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,监视卫星捕捉到了Celestial Being的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.59,0:16:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,MS队按照E3战术计划
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那台肩上有两个驱动装置的Gundam由我去迎战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要任何干涉和辅助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.42,0:16:45.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有何不可呢  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,久闻Mr.武士道大名  就让我们见识一下你的手段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我会回应你的期待  先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作战开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发现我们的敌人差不多该来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让Gundam先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.73,0:17:10.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一  第二甲板舱门开启
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Seravee  Arios  准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:16.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,电磁弹射器电压上升
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.06,0:17:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,射出时机移交给Seravee
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解  Seravee  特瑞亚·埃德  出发
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.41,0:17:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即使没有脑量子波…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,控制权移交
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确认控制权
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Arios  阿里路亚·哈普提兹姆  出发迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.07,0:17:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来  Cherudim和OO准备
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:47.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗  今天要认真打了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:48.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解  了解
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,电磁系统准备完成  发射时机移交
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.01,0:17:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Cherudim  洛克恩·斯托拉托斯  进行狙击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刹那  可别用TRANS-AM啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.85,0:18:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那架Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:08.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  现在还是想眼前的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,OO  刹那·F·清英  出发
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是要保护卡塔隆的各位吧  请让我也做点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:27.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的好意就心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,确认到A-LAWS的MS编队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即将进入战斗空域了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我得做点什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,捕捉到四架Gundam  现在分成小队进行各个击破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,双炉驱动的Gundam就交给你了  Mr.武士道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本小队的目标是长翅膀的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解  中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:59.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于等到这个时侯了  妈妈  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目视确认到Gundam了  全机开始攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,命中  命中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说过了  要认真打
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,实验体E-57！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.53,0:19:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是玛丽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.97,0:19:44.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.40,0:19:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别碍事！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:50.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈莱维准尉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自动攻击打不到敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.35,0:19:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶  要是里希提在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.06,0:20:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我到次舰桥去负责炮击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就集中精力操作舰体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:04.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让监视卫星捕捉到舰体然后凭力量强攻？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两台MS严重损坏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.00,0:20:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将战术转移到C计划
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.80,0:20:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.09,0:20:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是九条吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上校  请看武士道机！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有一架机体向OO突进！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,速度非常快！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那架新型机！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,射击也有长进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:34.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这就对了  少年！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.70,0:20:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小队长  哈莱维准尉前往敌人母舰了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.57,0:20:45.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在下去支援她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.25,0:20:51.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伊恩先生  请让我也帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你有觉悟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要保护那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:20:58.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  跟着来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.59,0:20:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.01,0:21:04.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太嫩了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是A-LAWS  难缠的机师可真多！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:14.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道操作方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.36,0:21:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两架敌机正向本舰靠近！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被突破了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.33,0:21:23.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开火  他们攻过来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在干什么  开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.41,0:21:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了人的话  我就跟你们一样了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.12,0:21:34.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了！  赶快！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗的话  又会伤害到无辜的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.71,0:21:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别…别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.01,0:21:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的行为应当被人怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:44.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子也是你们的牺牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.17,0:21:51.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Celestial Being！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.58,0:23:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你不尽全力  还是在侮辱我！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.04,0:23:36.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样  玛丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我  我是阿里路亚！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是超兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.01,0:23:44.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Gundam！  由我送你上路！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.67,0:23:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛…玛丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因阿里路亚和佩丽丝而暴露的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.23,0:24:05.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是与玛丽的再会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.49,0:24:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是与佩丽丝的离别
